{
  "name": "dashboard",
  "description": "Res.Publica Dashboard — a React + Vite + TypeScript single-page application that visualizes German and EU political data, including a Bundestag voting hemicycle, election analyses, legislation tracking, an EU law explorer, a lobby register, and an interactive MapLibre world map. It consumes a public Node API and ships a custom design system with light/dark themes and DE/EN i18n. Note: this project has over 100 source files; consider scoping analysis to a subdirectory for faster results.",
